			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">View source for CTF Flag State Blueprint (Unreal Tournament)</span></h1>
			<div id="bodyContent">
				<div id="contentSub">‚Üê <a href="/CTF_Flag_State_Blueprint_(Unreal_Tournament)" title="CTF Flag State Blueprint (Unreal Tournament)">CTF Flag State Blueprint (Unreal Tournament)</a></div>
